=== DRIFT_PROPHECY ===
# id: 66
# title: The Drift Prophecy
# chinese_title: 漂流预言
# category: Lore
# mode: dungeon

Carved into the station's chapel wall is a prophecy written in archaic Chinese characters: "When the dragon meets the phoenix in the space between spaces, the lost knowledge shall return." Below it, star coordinates have been scratched into the metal.

* [Copy the prophecy and coordinates]
  ~ gain_radical("龙")
  "龙" (lóng) — dragon
* [Meditate on the prophecy's meaning]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "预" (yù) — to predict, prophecy
* [Research the archaic characters]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "文" (wén) — text, writing, culture
